article_id:162,category_name:News,title_name:About Changes to Stamina and Getherwing Expenditure in Co-op,image_path:,message:<div>To make it easier to play co-op, in an update planned for the end of January 2019, we will make it so that the host will expend getherwings instead of stamina when playing co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>We will notify players again when preparations for the change described above have been made.</div><div><br></div><div>â–  Notes:</div><div>1. If you wish to purchase the 30-Day Pack (Recovery) which allows you to recover stamina and getherwings for 30 days from the purchase date, please be aware of this change in advance.</div><div>2. Stamina will be expended when playing single player or when using Skip Tickets.</div><div>3. The content described in this notification may change without warning.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing the Dragalia Lost game.</div>,start_time:1545302700,update_time1545302302